    • Method Detail

      • getId

        RDId getId()
        The fundamental interface for all review classes. All reviews are expected to have 3 items of core data:
        • RDId: A unique identifier
        • RDSubject: A subject
        • RDRating: A rating
        In addition, reviews may have some optional data:
        • RDComments: Comments
        • RDImages: Images
        • RDLocations: Locations
        • RDFacts: Facts
        • RDUrls: URLs
        Reviews can be trees with children sub-reviews ("criteria"), or be a sub-review with a parent review. They can be represented as a ReviewNode with zero or more children and/or a parent. Reviews may or may not be published (have non-null Author and Publish Date)
